msgid "Quickstart"
msgstr "快速入门"

msgid "Welcome to Ghostwriter! This platform streamlines security assessment reporting and team collaboration."
msgstr "欢迎使用 Ghostwriter！本平台用于简化安全评估报告流程与团队协作。"

msgid "Ghostwriter helps you manage the entire assessment lifecycle through:"
msgstr "Ghostwriter 通过以下功能协助管理评估全生命周期："

msgid "Client management and project tracking"
msgstr "客户管理与项目跟踪"

msgid "Findings library with reusable content"
msgstr "可复用内容的发现项库"

msgid "Infrastructure tracking for assessments"
msgstr "评估基础设施跟踪"

msgid "Report generation and collaboration with customizable templates"
msgstr "基于自定义模板的报告生成与协作"

msgid "To get started:"
msgstr "开始使用："

msgid "Explore existing clients and projects via the sidebar"
msgstr "通过侧边栏浏览已有客户与项目"

msgid "Set your active report to track your current work"
msgstr "设置当前报告以跟踪正在进行的工作"

msgid "Add findings to your report from the library or create custom ones"
msgstr "从库中添加发现项到报告，或创建自定义条目"

msgid "Generate reports with consistent formatting"
msgstr "生成格式统一的报告"

msgid "Use the sidebar navigation to access all features. This dashboard will show your assignments and project calendar events to keep you organized."
msgstr "使用侧边栏导航访问所有功能。本仪表板会显示分配给你的任务与项目日历事件，便于统筹安排。"

msgid "If you don't see any clients or projects, you may need to create them or request access. A manager or admin can assign you to an existing project to get you started. Once you have a project and a report, you can easily access them at any time from the left-hand sidebar available on every page."
msgstr "若未显示任何客户或项目，可能需要创建或申请访问权限。管理员可将你加入已有项目以便开始工作。获得项目和报告后，可随时通过每个页面左侧的侧边栏快速访问。"

msgid "Learn more from the <a href=\"https://ghostwriter.wiki/\" class=\"dashboard-link\">Ghostwriter Wiki</a>. Join our <a href=\"https://ghst.ly/BHSlack\" class=\"dashboard-link\">SpecterOps Slack Community</a> and the <em>#ghostwriter</em> channel to discuss Ghostwriter, ask questions, and get help."
msgstr "更多信息请访问 <a href=\"https://ghostwriter.wiki/\" class=\"dashboard-link\">Ghostwriter Wiki</a>。可加入 <a href=\"https://ghst.ly/BHSlack\" class=\"dashboard-link\">SpecterOps Slack 社区</a> 的 <em>#ghostwriter</em> 频道交流、提问与获取帮助。"

msgid "Don't Show This Again"
msgstr "不再显示"

msgid "Ready to Work?"
msgstr "准备开始工作？"

msgid "You're assigned to some active projects. Check those out here:"
msgstr "你已被分配到部分活跃项目，可在此查看："

msgid "Open the sidebar on the left to view/manage your reports under <em>My Active Reports</em>."
msgstr "打开左侧侧边栏，可在 <em>我的活跃报告</em> 中查看与管理报告。"

msgid "Select a report to mark it as active. If you're managing multiple reports, you can switch your active reports from there, too."
msgstr "选择一份报告将其标记为活跃报告。若同时管理多份报告，也可在此切换当前活跃报告。"

msgid "You're not assigned to any projects right now. If you're looking for a project, visit the <a class=\"dashboard-link\" href=\"%(projects_library_url)s\">Project Library</a>. You can also contact a manager or admin to get assigned to a project."
msgstr "当前未被分配到任何项目。如需查找项目，请访问 <a class=\"dashboard-link\" href=\"%(projects_library_url)s\">项目库</a>，也可联系管理员申请分配。"

